* LM741 Operational Amplifier Macro Model
* connections: N+ N- V+ V- OUT
.SUBCKT LM741 1 2 3 4 5
R741_IN 1 2 2MEG
*
* Differential transconductance: I = 0.1 * (V+ - V-)
* R741_GAIN at node 10 sets DC gain = 0.1 * 1MEG = 100k (100 dB)
* C741_POLE sets dominant pole at ~5.3 Hz
G741_DIFF 0 10 1 2 0.1
R741_GAIN 10 0 1MEG
C741_POLE 10 0 30P
*
* Supply clamping — hard clip at ~VCC+0.7V / VEE-0.7V
D741_CLP 10 3 DCLAMP
D741_CLN 4 10 DCLAMP
.MODEL DCLAMP D(IS=1E-15)
*
* Unity-gain output buffer
E741_OUT 5 0 10 0 1
R741_OUT 5 0 75
*
.ENDS LM741
